beer.beer_description:
Little Nipper uses a variety of hops that enable us to create a beer packed with fresh tropical fruit flavours. We use an English yeast strain to add an extra element of fruit, while keeping the beer rich and juicy.

Malt: Pale, Wheat, Oats
Hops: Varies with each batch
Appearance: Hazy sunshine
Aroma: Tropical fruits
Flavor: Passionfruit, mango, banana, citrus
Body: Full
